import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../Navbar'
import {HeroContainer, HeroContent, HeroItems, HeroH1, HeroP, HeroBtn} from './HeroElements'

const Hero = () => {
  return (
    <HeroContainer>
      <Navbar />
      <HeroContent>
        <HeroItems>
          <HeroH1>Have a taste of the Glory</HeroH1>
          <HeroP></HeroP>
          <HeroBtn>Place Order</HeroBtn>
        </HeroItems>
      </HeroContent>
    </HeroContainer>
  )
}

export default Hero
